Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.62,0:01:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,戌时已到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.60,0:01:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,犬夜叉马上要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.10,0:01:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,为了找齐四魂之玉碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.77,0:01:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,为了用这把铁碎牙打败奈落
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.24,0:01:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,与七人帮终于进入决战阶段
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.20,0:01:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,其中最后一位\N威力最大的亡魂  蛮骨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.27,0:01:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,他的大镰刀蛮龙\N跟犬夜叉那把铁碎牙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.05,0:01:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,马上就要展开激烈比划
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.02,0:01:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,弥勒法师  珊瑚七宝跟云母
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.75,0:01:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,穿梭于时空\N发生在战国时代与现代
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.05,0:01:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.02,0:01:44.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.15,0:01:51.15,OP,,0,0,0,,分散在蓝蓝天空上的 七颗星星
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.05,0:01:55.86,OP,,0,0,0,,每一颗星星 都刻着我的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.17,0:01:59.77,OP,,0,0,0,,就算梦想被粉碎 我也要寻找爱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.07,0:02:03.80,OP,,0,0,0,,我无处可逃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.02,0:02:07.87,OP,,0,0,0,,紧紧抓着我的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.10,0:02:16.30,OP,,0,0,0,,那些骗人的光阴 我再也不会输给它
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.37,0:02:21.67,OP,,0,0,0,,睁大眼睛 看清楚这瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.67,0:02:25.85,OP,,0,0,0,,它仍然紧紧围绕着我们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.12,0:02:29.85,OP,,0,0,0,,让人啜泣的 现实生活中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.85,0:02:33.85,OP,,0,0,0,,最重要的…到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.55,0:02:37.72,OP,,0,0,0,,繁忙的这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.72,0:02:41.95,OP,,0,0,0,,永恒的碎片 忽隐又忽现
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.95,0:02:45.87,OP,,0,0,0,,去触摸 去捕捉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.02,0:02:52.80,OP,,0,0,0,,我们就要循着目标继续向前走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.97,0:02:58.03,OP,,0,0,0,,为了得到最后的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.03,0:03:05.27,OP,,0,0,0,,我们就要循着目标继续向前走
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.59,0:03:20.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.42,0:03:24.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们几个是不是七人帮的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.89,0:03:27.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想不到瘦狼比笨狗来得更快
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.96,0:03:29.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.92,0:04:00.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别在那挣扎了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.79,0:04:02.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让开  瘦皮狼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.33,0:04:11.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于找到你们了吧  七人帮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.78,0:04:19.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第111话\N火星撞地球 蛮龙对风之伤
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.32,0:04:25.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.85,0:04:27.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少来烦我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.79,0:04:29.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来你就是犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.62,0:04:31.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到力气这么大
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.32,0:04:34.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是\N七人帮的最后一个对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.96,0:04:37.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  我是老大  蛮骨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.86,0:04:39.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臭家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.90,0:04:42.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该不会在那集众纠事\N欺负一只瘦皮狼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.20,0:04:43.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这只臭笨狗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.30,0:04:45.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以为我那么好欺负的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.74,0:04:46.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这小子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.67,0:04:48.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才你脚上那些四魂之玉碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.47,0:04:50.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差点就被抢走了  知不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.04,0:04:53.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会那么容易让人抢走吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.21,0:04:54.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.31,0:04:55.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钢牙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.48,0:04:57.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们怎么这么慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.65,0:04:59.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.75,0:05:01.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都到齐了是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.79,0:05:08.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们几个家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.79,0:05:12.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干了那么多伤天害理的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.73,0:05:15.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我就把你们\N一起送回坟墓去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.47,0:05:16.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.73,0:05:20.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要帮凶骨跟雾骨\N两兄弟讨个公道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.97,0:05:23.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看样子拿大镰刀的那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.54,0:05:24.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该就是他们的老大吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.74,0:05:27.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过他的长相最年轻呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.92,0:05:35.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.62,0:05:37.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心一点  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.69,0:05:40.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙\N脖子上有三块四魂之玉碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.93,0:05:41.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.70,0:05:45.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是雾骨跟凶骨的那份
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.93,0:05:49.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还真以为有三头六臂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.43,0:05:51.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是这么回事呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.27,0:05:54.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们身上的四魂之玉碎片\N一定是奈落给的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.84,0:05:57.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.28,0:05:59.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然会让你们几个杀人魔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.94,0:06:01.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重返人间
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.01,0:06:03.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这的确很像奈落的作风
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.02,0:06:04.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.08,0:06:07.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落要我们\N借着四魂之玉碎片的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.95,0:06:10.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把你们几个全都给消灭掉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.53,0:06:17.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我马上劈死你们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.86,0:06:20.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真有意思  尽管试试看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.87,0:06:27.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扭打起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.81,0:06:28.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不分轩轾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.61,0:06:31.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有闲情逸致在那看戏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.95,0:06:36.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.38,0:06:38.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.55,0:06:39.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.98,0:06:40.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.12,0:06:42.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要东张西望的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.19,0:06:46.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是多担心自己吧  臭小子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.63,0:06:51.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不要紧吧  戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.06,0:06:53.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.40,0:06:54.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还好没事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.90,0:06:56.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  钢牙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.57,0:06:58.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你总算做对了一件事\N没让戈薇受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.07,0:07:01.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臭笨狗  别用那种\N高高在上的口气跟我说话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.34,0:07:05.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  真的很谢谢你  钢牙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.34,0:07:07.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇  快找个地方躲起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.58,0:07:10.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些家伙\N想要我脚上的四魂之玉碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.98,0:07:11.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.42,0:07:18.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那个叫炼骨的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.92,0:07:20.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从我身上\N偷走了四魂之玉碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.86,0:07:23.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在还带在身上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.53,0:07:24.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.93,0:07:28.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个小姑娘她看得见\N我身上的四魂之玉碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.30,0:07:31.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臭家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.31,0:07:37.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上次隐瞒了这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.88,0:07:40.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万一让蛮骨大师兄发现的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.25,0:07:42.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看他恐怕不会放过我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.31,0:07:45.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,银骨  快杀了那个小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.55,0:07:47.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.62,0:07:48.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.19,0:07:51.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还不快跑  戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.12,0:07:53.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这就杀了你们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.63,0:07:56.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有那么容易吗  这混帐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.39,0:07:57.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钢牙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.20,0:08:02.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.63,0:08:04.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真以为可以打中我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.07,0:08:08.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,离那座大炮远一点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.54,0:08:10.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得把碎片抢回来才行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.48,0:08:11.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.78,0:08:14.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被那个家伙\N抢走的四魂之玉碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.21,0:08:15.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧  弥勒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.48,0:08:16.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.98,0:08:20.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你别想能够过去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.99,0:08:21.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡骨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.15,0:08:24.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天让老子陪你玩玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.42,0:08:27.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老子这辈子\N最恨的就是大夫跟和尚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.93,0:08:29.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你自己不也是大夫吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.16,0:08:34.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真要命  怎么又是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.17,0:08:36.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家一开始\N就挑到想要的对手了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.17,0:08:41.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道只留下这样的货色给我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.17,0:08:43.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我这种货色  还真抱歉喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.74,0:08:46.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陪女人过招\N我还真的没什么兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.51,0:08:50.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你给我死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.32,0:08:53.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少作梦了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.69,0:09:02.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不过是个半妖
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.53,0:09:04.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只比人类难缠一点而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.83,0:09:07.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不明白\N为什么奈落一直没有干掉你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.97,0:09:08.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.90,0:09:10.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙  只有这么点本事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.40,0:09:11.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臭小子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.40,0:09:15.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道奈落在哪里的话\N就赶快给我说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.97,0:09:18.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我懒得回答你这些问题
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.31,0:09:23.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你那么想知道\N奈落在什么地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.12,0:09:26.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就问问我这把蛮龙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.99,0:09:40.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好大一座山耶  邪见爷爷\N好不舒服啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.37,0:09:44.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么我非得\N大老远跑到这种地方不可
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.50,0:09:46.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  邪见爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.34,0:09:47.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得好难受
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.14,0:09:49.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.11,0:09:53.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道这座白灵山\N真的是圣地吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.75,0:09:55.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我们妖怪来说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.55,0:09:58.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这座山有一股干净到我们\N无法靠近的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.02,0:10:01.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小玲  你是个人类
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.25,0:10:02.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定感觉不出有任何异样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.55,0:10:04.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么感觉有人在拉我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.79,0:10:09.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再到前面看看吧  邪见爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.40,0:10:12.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本没在听嘛  这丫头
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.80,0:10:18.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完了  这下完了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.40,0:10:23.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天亡我也  天亡我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.95,0:10:33.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种地方\N应该不能容许奈落的妖气存在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.28,0:10:35.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀生丸少爷\N他为什么偏偏要…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.03,0:10:46.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是神圣的结界吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.40,0:10:48.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.27,0:10:52.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一路追踪奈落的手下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.84,0:10:56.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个叫琥珀的小鬼来到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.34,0:11:00.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如今气味就像消失了\N一点蛛丝马迹都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.49,0:11:15.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好慢哦  杀生丸少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.59,0:11:18.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真想早点离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.23,0:11:19.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底跑去哪里了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.10,0:11:21.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少爷会不会来救我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.94,0:11:25.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.24,0:11:28.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.11,0:11:31.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  是琥珀哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.98,0:11:37.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回来  小玲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.32,0:11:39.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能一个人到处乱跑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.15,0:11:42.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别害我被杀生丸少爷骂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.12,0:11:46.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差一点就被结界给消灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.53,0:11:48.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小玲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.89,0:11:49.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.55,0:12:10.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀哥哥  琥珀哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.28,0:12:12.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.28,0:12:15.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了  终于又见到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.15,0:12:17.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小玲  你怎么会到这来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.06,0:12:20.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上次莫名其妙就跟你分开了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.66,0:12:22.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直好担心你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.53,0:12:23.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.49,0:12:25.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里不是你该来的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.80,0:12:28.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.00,0:12:30.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别出声
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.64,0:12:37.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在慢慢的走回去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.94,0:12:39.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁他们还没有发现你之前
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.91,0:12:40.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.55,0:12:42.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.41,0:12:44.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万一被发现\N你会被他们给吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.18,0:12:46.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀哥哥  你不走吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.02,0:12:48.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些家伙不会攻击我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.05,0:12:50.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.79,0:12:54.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.60,0:13:06.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去死吧  臭和尚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.34,0:13:08.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可没那么容易就会死
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.58,0:13:11.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒法师
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.34,0:13:13.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别东张西望行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.69,0:13:24.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让地狱的烈火烧死你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.96,0:13:26.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会怕你这点小把戏吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.10,0:13:32.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.23,0:13:33.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臭家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.97,0:13:38.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落的毒虫出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.97,0:13:39.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是最猛胜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.64,0:13:41.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道在叫我们撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.87,0:13:43.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.48,0:13:45.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烦不烦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.61,0:13:47.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等我收拾完\N这几个家伙再说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.51,0:13:49.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本来想再多陪你们过几招的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.11,0:13:50.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.12,0:13:52.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就先留着你那条狗命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.25,0:13:54.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这话应该我说才对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.12,0:13:57.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看招  风之伤
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.59,0:14:00.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在才跑太迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.13,0:14:04.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是风之伤
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.01,0:14:15.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蛮骨大师兄
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.24,0:14:16.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.02,0:14:26.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道我的厉害了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.39,0:14:29.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.89,0:14:33.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然敢打伤我的蛮龙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.29,0:14:35.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,银骨  你做得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.03,0:14:37.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚多亏你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.26,0:14:41.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.67,0:14:45.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉\N今天就陪你玩到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.64,0:14:47.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙别想走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.51,0:14:49.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少在那悠闲地喝酒了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.84,0:14:51.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中计了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.81,0:14:58.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唯独这个女人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.95,0:14:59.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.08,0:15:02.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要尽快把她杀了\N以免横生枝节
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.32,0:15:04.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.02,0:15:06.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.23,0:15:10.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.70,0:15:15.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炼骨  这次你休想逃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.87,0:15:23.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.88,0:15:29.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也未免太夸张了一点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.55,0:15:32.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看样子是希望\N我们尽快赶回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.68,0:15:33.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次见了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.12,0:15:37.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们这些人  休想逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.73,0:15:52.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉  好久不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.14,0:15:55.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈…奈落
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.98,0:16:03.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.12,0:16:05.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原谅我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.62,0:16:08.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求求你原谅我  杀生丸少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.15,0:16:10.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还来不及阻止小玲  她就…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.42,0:16:15.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是说小玲\N跑进结界了是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.80,0:16:19.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千万别这么做  杀生丸少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.80,0:16:23.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一踏进圣地\N马上就会被消灭的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.77,0:16:24.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别罗唆了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.80,0:16:26.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看看后面
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.91,0:16:30.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  是小玲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.01,0:16:33.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀生丸少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.01,0:16:36.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀也在里面是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.29,0:16:43.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可要老老实实的回答少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.05,0:16:46.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,任何事情\N都别想瞒过我们的少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.82,0:16:50.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道杀生丸少爷\N真的要杀了琥珀哥哥吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.66,0:16:52.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事…事情是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.06,0:16:55.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是琥珀帮助小玲逃出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.17,0:16:57.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洞窟里面有好多好多妖怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.84,0:17:00.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么  有妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.47,0:17:04.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀哥哥一直保护小玲\N不被妖怪吃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.48,0:17:06.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…所以
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.14,0:17:09.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣地里怎么会有妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.58,0:17:12.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀生丸少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.55,0:17:13.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.45,0:17:16.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是奈落在故布疑阵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.32,0:17:23.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们这些笨蛋\N总算找到这来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.19,0:17:24.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.00,0:17:27.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉  这个奈落恐怕是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.10,0:17:29.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用说一定是傀儡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.70,0:17:32.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是想多争取一点时间\N好让七人帮跑掉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.01,0:17:36.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪  怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.11,0:17:39.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个真的是傀儡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.48,0:17:40.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.44,0:17:42.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一定是奈落\N故意放出来的傀儡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.08,0:17:44.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么啊  戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.72,0:17:49.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是  跟以前那些傀儡\N似乎有些不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.69,0:17:52.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之是假的  没什么用
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.69,0:17:53.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钢牙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.80,0:18:05.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,任何人也别想过去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.37,0:18:08.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然变得这么大
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.31,0:18:09.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.27,0:18:10.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.14,0:18:14.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种纸老虎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.68,0:18:16.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风之伤
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.62,0:18:29.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁也别想过去…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.66,0:18:31.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好极了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.86,0:18:34.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钢牙  你想抢功是不是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.70,0:18:36.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少废话  臭笨狗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.33,0:18:37.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续跟着你这个慢吞吞的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.07,0:18:40.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七人帮早就逃到老远了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.91,0:18:43.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这帮坏蛋\N应该还在这附近才对
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.71,0:18:44.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次我不会让你们跑掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.84,0:18:47.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臭小子  你给我站住
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.11,0:18:49.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.61,0:18:52.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇姑娘发现了什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.82,0:18:54.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  你们几个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.65,0:18:56.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个傀儡真的好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.75,0:18:58.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像太干净了一点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.32,0:19:00.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落的傀儡居然会太干净
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.82,0:19:01.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.16,0:19:03.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很像
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.43,0:19:05.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟白灵山的感觉很像
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.33,0:19:06.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白灵山
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.70,0:19:09.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么?这味道怎么会这么香
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.00,0:19:14.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个傀儡有水跟花的香味
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.37,0:19:15.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水跟花的香味
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.44,0:19:17.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一点都没错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.84,0:19:21.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过奈落的傀儡\N为什么会发出这种香味来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.15,0:19:28.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们这些坏蛋\N到底躲到哪里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.42,0:19:31.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.69,0:19:35.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是结界
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.79,0:19:37.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.00,0:19:41.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于看见了  蛮骨大师兄
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.57,0:19:42.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白灵山就到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.53,0:19:46.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过这股空气真是奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.54,0:19:49.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比上次来的时候\N更让人不舒服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.74,0:19:51.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这边一点都感觉不到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.01,0:19:55.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想应该是\N圣地的结界太强了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.25,0:19:56.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信这么一来\N犬夜叉跟钢牙那两个小子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.01,0:19:58.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都没有办法追过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.92,0:19:59.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.42,0:20:02.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连我们都觉得不舒服\N好歹我们还是人类呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.49,0:20:05.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.76,0:20:10.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来不需要劳师动众\N跑到山脚下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.53,0:20:15.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蛮骨大爷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.03,0:20:17.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你啊  琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.43,0:20:19.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个惨白的小鬼是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.34,0:20:20.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是神无
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.24,0:20:24.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.11,0:20:29.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.21,0:20:30.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你认得他
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.68,0:20:33.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,错不了的\N雾骨就是他干掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.85,0:20:36.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是犬夜叉的哥哥叫杀生丸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.32,0:20:39.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是犬夜叉的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.59,0:20:40.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.09,0:20:42.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.43,0:20:44.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他也是我们要杀的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.06,0:20:47.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道就为了跟我们说这些
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.56,0:20:49.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大老远把我们找回来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.80,0:20:51.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才差点就干掉犬夜叉了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.00,0:20:55.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再跟他纠缠下去\N你会被他杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.81,0:20:59.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在胡说什么  小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.54,0:21:02.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就凭蛮骨那把大镰刀\N是打不过犬夜叉的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.05,0:21:10.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是指\N我这把蛮龙挂了彩的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.25,0:21:11.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这点小伤不算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.06,0:21:14.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须变得更厉害一点
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.97,0:21:23.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是这么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.60,0:21:26.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炼骨\N我看你还是乖乖交出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.50,0:21:27.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我全都知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.34,0:21:29.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是指什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.04,0:21:32.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说我全都知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.78,0:21:35.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你把上次从那个\N叫戈薇的女孩身上偷来的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.85,0:21:37.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四魂之玉碎片给藏了起来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.58,0:21:40.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是说\N你脖子上的四魂之玉碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.52,0:21:43.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要我划开取出吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.32,0:21:46.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你先别发火  大师兄
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.76,0:21:48.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我原本就想要交给你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.33,0:21:53.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算你聪明嘛  炼骨
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.40,0:21:55.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,几个兄弟里面\N果然你的脑筋最灵光了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.10,0:21:57.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不过
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.94,0:21:59.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望不要有下一次
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.21,0:22:02.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.84,0:22:04.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那好  那么睡骨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.78,0:22:07.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有蛇骨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.14,0:22:10.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两个\N马上帮我干掉杀生丸那小子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.32,0:22:12.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不服气吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.58,0:22:14.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是一向最喜欢男人的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.45,0:22:17.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只喜欢犬夜叉一个\N到底要人家说几次嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.96,0:22:19.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不过是你一厢情愿罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.89,0:22:21.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死了这条心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.29,0:22:23.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉由我来解决
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.03,0:22:26.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.64,0:22:34.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很不错
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.04,0:22:37.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经查出\N犬夜叉所在的位置了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.67,0:22:39.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真不愧是个奸细呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.91,0:22:42.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不是奸细
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.92,0:22:47.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个半妖混帐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.55,0:22:51.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洗干净脑袋等着瞧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.93,0:22:58.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到水边
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.83,0:23:00.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道要搜河流跟沼泽吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.17,0:23:04.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从来没有闻过
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.10,0:23:06.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种水味跟花香
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.00,0:23:10.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确\N从来没有闻过这样的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.17,0:23:12.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是七人帮这件事怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.84,0:23:14.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要我们继续追查奈落
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.18,0:23:16.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七人帮迟早会现身的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.38,0:23:19.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落那混帐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.25,0:23:21.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我发誓非把你找出来不可
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.65,0:24:56.65,ED,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.22,0:23:32.20,ED,,0,0,0,,偷偷亲你一下 装作若无其事的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.20,0:23:37.27,ED,,0,0,0,,我这样调皮 是不是像个孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.55,0:23:43.70,ED,,0,0,0,,早已习惯 被你说是娇嗔无理
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.70,0:23:53.42,ED,,0,0,0,,不过「喜欢你」这三个字却始终说不出口 My Sweet Emotion
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.40,0:24:04.35,ED,,0,0,0,,对着镜子 多看一次 看看自己的微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.12,0:24:17.65,ED,,0,0,0,,如果想飞奔出去追求刺激就得挺起胸膛向前走
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.02,0:24:28.55,ED,,0,0,0,,大胆放手去做 直到满意为止
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.72,0:24:37.60,ED,,0,0,0,,偷偷亲你一下 装作若无其事的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.60,0:24:42.77,ED,,0,0,0,,我这样调皮 是不是像个孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.07,0:24:49.35,ED,,0,0,0,,早已习惯 被你说是娇嗔无理
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.35,0:24:58.82,ED,,0,0,0,,不过「喜欢你」这三个字却始终说不出口 My Sweet Emotion
